This folder is for replicating the project made by Andrej Karpathy on making a mini ChatGPT model. 
link to the original project: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kCc8FmEb1nY&
The model is trained on this dataset: https://github.com/karpathy/char-rnn/blob/master/data/tinyshakespeare/input.txt
Just before undertaking this project, I wrote an article on how Transformes work. Check it out here: https://medium.com/@larsmartinbg/the-technical-abcs-of-transformers-in-deep-learning-df1b1b8b50dd



mapping from characters to integers is very simple. Other options include TikToken